lead_paragraph: Manchester United manager Jose Mourinho has said he has struggled to adapt to life in Manchester, labelling his living arrangement in the city as "bit of a disaster".

headline.print_headline: Life in Manchester 'Bit of a Disaster', Says Mourinho
